---
---

<section class="hero-section section-surface">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">CloudBridge Networks</p>
        <p class="hero-kicker">Satellite-backed network infrastructure across Africa.</p>
        <h1>A reliable network needs more than a dish on the roof.</h1>
        <p class="hero-intro">
          CloudBridge builds and operates internet infrastructure for hospitals, institutions,
          businesses, and remote sites that cannot depend on weak terrestrial coverage alone.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-support">
          We design the backhaul, distribute service across the site, run billing and access,
          and stay responsible after launch.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Talk to our team</a>
          <a href="/#mission" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn how we work</a>
        </div>

        <p class="hero-note">One team accountable from first survey to daily service.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-panel card" aria-label="CloudBridge operating model">
        <div class="hero-panel-header">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Operating model</p>
            <h2 class="hero-panel-title">One delivery path from satellite link to daily support.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-panel-tag">Built for real sites</p>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-stage-grid">
          <article class="hero-stage">
            <p class="hero-stage-index">01</p>
            <h3>Backhaul</h3>
            <p>Satellite capacity planned around the site, location, and expected load.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="hero-stage">
            <p class="hero-stage-index">02</p>
            <h3>On-site network</h3>
            <p>Coverage that extends beyond the roofline and reaches the people using the service.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="hero-stage">
            <p class="hero-stage-index">03</p>
            <h3>Billing and access</h3>
            <p>Usage, account control, and service rules handled as part of the rollout.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="hero-stage">
            <p class="hero-stage-index">04</p>
            <h3>Ongoing operation</h3>
            <p>Monitoring, issue response, and support after the network is live.</p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-panel-footer">
          <p class="hero-panel-label">Where we work</p>
          <div class="hero-sector-list" aria-label="CloudBridge site types">
            <span>Hospitals</span>
            <span>Institutions</span>
            <span>Business sites</span>
            <span>Remote facilities</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding-top: var(--space-96);
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-24);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .hero-copy .eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .hero-copy h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    max-width: 620px;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4.2vw, 3.9rem);
    line-height: 1.04;
  }

  .hero-intro {
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.72;
  }

  .hero-support {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-top: var(--space-16);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-12);
    margin-top: var(--space-24);
  }

  .hero-note {
    margin-top: var(--space-32);
    max-width: 520px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-subtle);
  }

  .hero-panel {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-panel-header {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    padding: var(--space-24);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero-panel-title {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    max-width: 420px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.18;
  }

  .hero-panel-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 32px;
    padding: 0 var(--space-12);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-control);
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .hero-stage-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .hero-stage {
    padding: var(--space-24);
    min-height: 188px;
  }

  .hero-stage:nth-child(odd) {
    border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero-stage:nth-child(n + 3) {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero-stage-index {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-subtle);
  }

  .hero-stage h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero-panel-footer {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    padding: var(--space-24);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero-panel-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-subtle);
  }

  .hero-sector-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .hero-sector-list span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 34px;
    padding: 0 var(--space-12);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-control);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (min-width: 980px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.98fr) minmax(420px, 1.02fr);
      gap: var(--space-32);
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-section {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 81px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-panel-header {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .hero-stage-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .hero-section {
      padding-top: var(--space-64);
    }

    .hero-intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-stage {
      min-height: 0;
    }

    .hero-stage:nth-child(odd) {
      border-right: 0;
    }

    .hero-stage + .hero-stage {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
  }
</style>
